        <h2 class="artical-title">Are Lab-Grown Diamonds for Me?</h2>
        <p>Diamonds have always been regarded as a symbol of everlasting love and affection. Over the years, they’ve
            become everybody’s best friend and their demand has increased. But there have also been several concerns
            regarding the way diamonds are mined and the impact it has on us and the environment. For the conscious
            consumer, lab-grown diamonds are a fabulous alternative. These engineered diamonds are 100% real and are
            lighter on your wallet and your conscience. If you’re wondering what makes lab-grown diamonds the right
            choice for you, let’s take a look at a few facts.</p>
